{"tid":1918082,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"法國文化部長感染武漢肺炎","createTime":"2020-03-10T01:02:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-10T01:18:51.000Z","uid":14918,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"bc3944df149155ec9ebf530e97105c7aa330f693","tid":1918082,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T01:02:33.000Z","msg":"（中央社巴黎9日電）法國文化部長辦公室晚間發出聲明，部長里斯特確認感染武漢肺炎，目前身體狀況良好。衛生部公衛署長沙羅孟宣布，今天新增286名確診病例，累計1412人，其中25人死。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n法國文化部長里斯特（Franck Riester）辦公室今晚向法新社表示，里斯特確認感染2019年冠狀病毒疾病（COVID-19，武漢肺炎），但強調他的身體狀況良好，並在巴黎家中。<br />\n<br />\n里斯特辦公室表示，「部長日前出現病徵，今天病毒檢測結果為陽性」，並指出上週部長曾出席已有數人遭感染的國民議會<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"145b39f8df07d887e7eeaddd40733f9361d19ecd","tid":1918082,"uid":229185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T01:03:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d62846d0a51445aeb6df79231e970f0653e6020","tid":1918082,"uid":39167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T01:03:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fae296811a63cc92fa85bd2d580b8e3700fd80d5","tid":1918082,"uid":27146,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T01:04:12.000Z","msg":"賤種男版777馬克龍幾時中招？"},{"pid":"1c5b48084e6381be08f39877bd2c682ca2162c2a","tid":1918082,"uid":105567,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T01:05:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media0.giphy.com/media/V0BYQVxPPpTdS/source.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia0.gip